name: Bunny Brown vs The Bake Sale
name_original: Bunny Brown vs The Bake Sale
description:
Episode 3, Bunny Brown vs The Bake Sale: this time, Bunny puts on her chef's hat and takes part in a bake sale for her perpetually underfunded public school.  Of course there is an incident...
